tion":0},"title":"Hadith on Rights: Every claimant is entitled to speak","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, seeking the settlement of his loans and he spoke harshly to him. This disturbed his companions, but the Prophet said, \u201cLeave him alone, for everyone with a right is entitled to speak.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/21\/ramadan-make-up-missed-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":33408,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Making up missed fasts throughout the year","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salamah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cI had to make up some fasts I missed during the month of Ramadan, but I was unable to do so until the month of Sha\u2019ban as\u00a0I was busy with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27596,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/menses-missed-sawm-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":33408,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Menses: Women make up missed fasts, not prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adhah reported: I asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, \u201cWhy do menstruating women make up missed fasts but not missed prayers?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWhen we were afflicted with menstruation, we were ordered to make up missed fasts but not missed prayers.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 335 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25470,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/29\/using-vessels-kuffar-mushrikin\/","url_meta":{"origin":33408,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Utensils: Using the dishware of idolaters if necessary","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Imran ibn Hussein reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and his companions performed ablution from the waterskin of an idolatrous woman. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 337, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 682 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u064f\u0635\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u0644\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27609,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/15\/fasting-on-behalf-of-deceased\/","url_meta":{"origin":33408,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Making up missed fasts on behalf of deceased","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A woman came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and she said, \u201cMy mother has died and she owed a month of fasting.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cDo you think if she had a debt you would repay it on her behalf?\u201d She\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37044,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/09\/28\/hayd-fasts-not-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":33408,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hayd: Menstruating women make up fasts, but not prayers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adhah reported: I asked Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, saying, \u201cWhy do menstruating women make up missed fasts but not missed prayers?\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWe endured those menses and we were ordered to make up missed fasts, but we were not ordered to make up missed prayers.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33408","targetHints":